creator: House of HR
descriptionHtml:
Looking for a job?
Want some extra cash by working in bars, shops or on events? With NOWJOBS you get tailored made jobs. You decide where and when you want to work. Your net amount is transparent and known from the start! And your well-earned cash will be deposited on your bank account the next working day. Ka-tching!
NOWJOBS is a start-up supported by temp and selection agency Accent and is responsible for the compliant handling of all admin and payments, therefore: no surprises. All ‘paperwork’ is now digital, or more precisely mobile, and that without having to leave your house.
After the job you give a review to the company, and just like that you are ready for your next job.

You’re an employer and looking URGENTLY for help?
As an employer you desire to find extra help as smooth as possible, even when it’s unexpected or outside business hours.
In a couple of seconds you create a vacancy. Next, you send the vacancy to all available candidates or your favorites.
You receive only the profiles of those interested candidates, and we show you immediately in all transparency the cost of the profile. Only confirming and sending the contract remains, and the deal is closed.
Accent, temp and selection agency, is responsible for all admin related to the contract, payments of the candidate and invoicing.
The moment de job is finished, you can review the candidate. You’ll also see the his/her review about your company. So, put on your biggest smile, and without a doubt your company will be the favorite with 5 stars.
descriptionShort: Need extra cash? Start a NOWJOB now!

With NOWJOBS you get tailored made jobs. You decide where and when you want to work. Your salary is transparent and known from the start! And your well-earned cash will be deposited on your bank account in a few days. Ka-tching!

You’re an employer and looking for help?
As an employer you desire to find extra help as smooth as possible, even when it’s unexpected or outside business hours. In a couple of seconds you create a vacancy. Next, you send the vacancy to all available candidates or your favorites.
You receive only the profiles of those interested candidates, and we show you immediately in all transparency the cost of the profile. Only confirming and sending the contract remains, and the deal is closed.

title:
NOWJOBS
11.5.0

creator: House of HR
descriptionHtml:
Looking for a job?
With NOWJOBS you get tailored made jobs. You decide where and when you want to work. Your salary is transparent and known from the start! And your well-earned cash will be deposited on your bank account in a few days. Ka-tching!

You’re an employer and looking for help?
As an employer you desire to find extra help as smooth as possible, even when it’s unexpected or outside business hours. In a couple of seconds you create a vacancy. Next, you send the vacancy to all available candidates or your favorites.
You receive only the profiles of those interested candidates, and we show you immediately in all transparency the cost of the profile. Only confirming and sending the contract remains, and the deal is closed.
descriptionShort: Need extra cash? Start a NOWJOB now!

title:
NOWJOBS
11.20.0

creator: House of HR
descriptionHtml:
Find employees or find your student job or flexi-job with NOWJOBS! More than 25.000 employers use the NOWJOBS app to post vacancies and register flexible staff, without administrative burden. More than 600,000 flexis and students find the ideal job via the app, wherever and whenever they want: from hospitality to industry, from weekend jobs to summer jobs!

Student workers and flexi-jobbers – extra income and unique job opportunities? With the NOWJOBS app, you decide where, when and how often you work! Swipe through the vacancies for jobs in your area & find the job that fits your schedule! We’ve got it all:

- Student jobs, flexi-jobs, weekend jobs, summer jobs or side jobs.
- Swipe, work and get paid within a week.
- 24/7. You decide when you work: your ideal job is at your fingertips.

Download the NOWJOBS app & get the job done!

Employers – Recruitment or payroll? The NOWJOBS app has everything you need. You post vacancies for free and register the ideal student worker or flexi-jobber, up to 2 hours before the shift starts. Find employees today and pay after the shift is done! We'll take care of the administration.

- Free vacancies. You post vacancies for free and watch the responses flow in. You only pay after the shift.
- A flexible team. Add the greatest candidates to your team. This way you can use them when the need is greatest.
- Administrative relief. From contract proposal to Dimona declaration: NOWJOBS takes care of it!

Download the NOWJOBS app & get the job done!
descriptionShort: The app for flexis and students. Find work or post vacancies. Your choice!
